func simulate(stone S: Int, wood W: Int, ore Q: Int, boxes B: Int, lv: Int) -> (ok: Bool, log: [String], remaining: (stone:Int, wood:Int, ore:Int)?) {
    var stone = S, wood = W, ore = Q, box = B
    var log: [String] = []
    
    let needStone = 1260 * lv
    let needWood  = 340 * lv
    let needOre   = 130 * lv
    
    var need: Int
    var use: Int
    var stoneNeed: Int
    var possible: Int
    
    // Box ‚Üí ore
    need = max(0, needOre - ore)
    use = min(box, need)
    if use > 0 { log.append("D√πng \(use) h·ªôp ‚Üí +\(use) qu·∫∑ng") }
    ore += use; box -= use
    
    // Box ‚Üí wood
    need = max(0, needWood - wood)
    use = min(box, Int(ceil(Double(need)/4)))
    if use > 0 { log.append("D√πng \(use) h·ªôp ‚Üí +\(use*4) g·ªó") }
    wood += use*4; box -= use
    
    // Box ‚Üí stone
    if box > 0 { log.append("D√πng \(box) h·ªôp ‚Üí +\(box*20) ƒë√°") }
    stone += box*20; box = 0
    
    // Wood ‚Üí ore
    need = max(0, needOre - ore)
    possible = wood/4
    use = min(need, possible)
    if use>0 { log.append("ƒê·ªïi \(use*4) g·ªó ‚Üí +\(use) qu·∫∑ng") }
    wood -= use*4; ore += use
    
    // Stone ‚Üí ore
    need = max(0, needOre - ore)
    stoneNeed = need*20
    if need>0 { log.append("ƒê·ªïi \(stoneNeed) ƒë√° ‚Üí +\(need) qu·∫∑ng") }
    if stone < stoneNeed { return (false, log, nil) }
    stone -= stoneNeed; ore += need
    
    // Stone ‚Üí wood
    need = max(0, needWood - wood)
    stoneNeed = need*5
    if need>0 { log.append("ƒê·ªïi \(stoneNeed) ƒë√° ‚Üí +\(need) g·ªó") }
    if stone < stoneNeed { return (false, log, nil) }
    stone -= stoneNeed; wood += need
    
    if stone<needStone || wood<needWood || ore<needOre { return (false, log, nil) }
    
    stone -= needStone; wood -= needWood; ore -= needOre
    
    return (true, log, (stone, wood, ore))
}

func computeLv() {

// Logic simulate
function simulate(S,W,Q,B,lv){
    let stone=S,wood=W,ore=Q,box=B,log=[];
    const needStone=1260*lv, needWood=340*lv, needOre=130*lv;
    let need,use,stoneNeed,possible;

    need=Math.max(0,needOre-ore); use=Math.min(box,need);
    if(use>0) log.push(`D√πng ${use} h·ªôp ‚Üí +${use} qu·∫∑ng`); ore+=use; box-=use;

    need=Math.max(0,needWood-wood); use=Math.min(box,Math.ceil(need/4));
    if(use>0) log.push(`D√πng ${use} h·ªôp ‚Üí +${use*4} g·ªó`); wood+=use*4; box-=use;

    if(box>0) log.push(`D√πng ${box} h·ªôp ‚Üí +${box*20} ƒë√°`); stone+=box*20; box=0;

    need=Math.max(0,needOre-ore); possible=Math.floor(wood/4); use=Math.min(need,possible);
    if(use>0) log.push(`ƒê·ªïi ${use*4} g·ªó ‚Üí +${use} qu·∫∑ng`); wood-=use*4; ore+=use;

    need=Math.max(0,needOre-ore); stoneNeed=need*20; if(need>0) log.push(`ƒê·ªïi ${stoneNeed} ƒë√° ‚Üí +${need} qu·∫∑ng`);
    if(stone<stoneNeed) return {ok:false,log}; stone-=stoneNeed; ore+=need;

    need=Math.max(0,needWood-wood); stoneNeed=need*5; if(need>0) log.push(`ƒê·ªïi ${stoneNeed} ƒë√° ‚Üí +${need} g·ªó`);
    if(stone<stoneNeed) return {ok:false,log}; stone-=stoneNeed; wood+=need;

    if(stone<needStone||wood<needWood||ore<needOre) return {ok:false,log};
    stone-=needStone; wood-=needWood; ore-=needOre;

    return {ok:true,log,remaining:{stone,wood,ore}};
}

// computeLv
function computeLv(){
    let S=Number(document.getElementById('stone').value)||0;
    let W=Number(document.getElementById('wood').value)||0;
    let Q=Number(document.getElementById('ore').value)||0;
    let B=Number(document.getElementById('boxes').value)||0;

    let lo=0, hi=20000, lastLog=[], lastRemaining=null;
    while(lo<hi){

        let result=simulate(S,W,Q,B,mid);
        if(result.ok){ lo=mid; lastLog=result.log; lastRemaining=result.remaining; }

    }

    const out=document.getElementById('output'); out.style.display='block';

            ƒê√°: ${lastRemaining.stone} | G·ªó: ${lastRemaining.wood} | Qu·∫∑ng: ${lastRemaining.ore}

    } else { out.innerHTML="Kh√¥ng ƒë·ªß t√†i nguy√™n ƒë·ªÉ n√¢ng c·∫•p"; }
